liteamp (0.3.1-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * new features:
   - library(by genre, artist, album and playlist) management support
   - ID3V2 and vorbis comment editing support
   - album artwork support
   - visualizer support
  * dependencies changes:
   - requires gtk+ 2.4
   - not requires libgnome and libgnomeui
  * many new features with new bugs ;)

 -- Dongsu Jang <iolo@hellocity.net>  Fri, 7 May 2004 00:00:00 +0900

