liteamp (0.2.3-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * backports tag parser from devel tree.
    - use libid3tag
    - "tag_codesets" added to prefs to provide fallback tag codesets
  * remove useless "All" playlist
    - it'll be back in the next major version with useful features.

